  - guid: 66cb566e-46dc-4ec9-8684-a672de76bfb1
    dialogue:
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: There will be some guys on my side on the next round.
        They are smaller than me, so do not worry.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: Look at their eye when you beat them up. Red eyes
        mean they can not take much more.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: Maybe take them out before fighting me or it could
        get overwhelming.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: Oh, and when your camera is locked on, you can SWITCH
        TARGETS. Makes it easier to focus.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    position: {x: 1299, y: 200}
    transitionNode: 1
    entryPoint: 0
    isCheckpoint: 0
    disableAlreadyChosenOptions: 0
  - guid: f27e40b4-e2c3-4db5-9241-fbbea1bf83af
    dialogue:
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: Thank you. I will give it my all next time.
